Almost new industrial unit for lease near Myaree.

Excellent small commercial unit.

Flexible lease terms on offer.

Air-conditioned office with storage area.

This represents an opportunity to lease a property with upstairs offices and down stairs storage.

Exceptional lease terms are on offer for this 259 sqm property. Office is approx.. 159 sqm with storage of approx.. 100 sqm.

The property enjoys excellent exposure to Marmion Road.

Please call Geoff Fraser 0413 624 000

CBRE and LJ Hooker Commercial are pleased to present 17, 11B & 11C Aldous Place, Booragoon for sale. The property provides an exceptional investment with a pre-existing long-term lease to ENJO Australia.

Located in the thriving, tightly-held commercial, retail and industrial precinct of Booragoon, this versatile office/ warehouse facility is located only 13km's south-west of the Perth CBD.

The property consists of an impressive office, warehouse and training facility across three separate titles which offer both investment security and longer term diversity.

For Sale via Offers to Purchase Invited closing Wednesday 1st June 2016 at 3.00PM AWST.

*approx.

Booragoon is situated approximately 15kms from Perth's CBD and is located between major arterial roads, Canning and Leach Highways and Kwinana Freeway.

Ground floor office adjacent to Garden City Shopping Centre.

546 sqm approx plus 10 car bays.

Well presented, includes reception, several partitioned offices, open plan offices, separate male and female toilets and lunchroom.

Zoned "Commercial" by the City of Melville.

Short Term Leaseback available.

Suit Occupier or Investor.
